phrases: TL Note: This is a pun on Souieba (being told that) and Souireba (dentures).
Pyramid-text: Guy forcing tributes Woman Guy who pays tribute Out of the question
Geez, it sure is raining hard.
It is so damp and disgusting.
So that means the entire Honshu region is now in the rainy season.
That is what they say.
The weather will be unstable everywhere,
so please be on the lookout for sudden gusts, lightning, swollen rivers, and landslides.
It is going to be raining hard for a while.
Doing the laundry and stuff is going to get so tiresome.
Ah, I will answer it.
What happened?
Did not you head straight home?
Well, I did but...
Oh, you can use the dryer.
Thanks...
So nice...
So like I said, I did head straight home.
But I noticed...
that I had forgotten the keys to my house.
I checked thoroughly whether the windows were locked or not.
From the bathroom windows to the ones on the second floor.
That was when I noticed a policeman waiting for me with his nightstick.
I explained that it was my house but I was taken to the police box.
Hey, do I really look like a criminal?
I would rather get pointed at with a nightstick!
I want to scare an adult!
But little children will be frightened too!
I am jealous!
So freaking jealous!
Why are our builds so different when we have lived the same amount of time?
I want to be seen as a high school student for once!
I feel the same way too!
I am sorry my clothes do not fit you.
No, this is fine.
Your father's was in the closet.
Oh, was it?
Which one?
The one on the left...
They really are living together.
Which one?
You see, not that one but...
It feels strange.
Deeper inside...
Do not stick to me so much!
That is because you are so dull.
You are so perverted these days.
Like the Maid Cafe thing the other day.
I-It is normal for a healthy boy!
Why am I getting all embarrassed?
It is just a conversation between a good brother and sister.
A normal inter-personal contact,
between people of such harmonious, prime aged...
siblings...?
In the first place, you are...
Are they?
What about that?
But Jin, I am doing it for you-
It is not that!
It is not that...
Your clothes are too cute...
Too indecent...
I cannot look at you straight, so I am telling you to stand back!
Realize that, you idiot!
It is even more unnatural to easily accept a sister who suddenly showed up.
Cannot it be helped that he can only look at her as a woman?
But, that means...
A forbidden love?!
Am I dressed that cutely and indecently?
Yeah.
I cannot look directly at you.
But I am your sister...
Are not you even more indecent for looking at your own sister in such a way?
But I cannot help myself,
since you are so cute...
J-Jin...!
Putting that aside, it is your birthday today.
I bought you a birthday cake.
Could it be that to buy that cake...
you have been working part time at the maid cafe?
It is not like that...
It was just on a whim.
Do not get the wrong idea, okay?
Thank you, Neesan.
This is the first time you have called me Neesan...
But...
Huh?
What is this...?
Why does my heart hurt so much?
It must be...
the same reason why I do not want to call you Neesan either.
Jin...
Neesan, I actually love you as a woman.
Even if we are siblings, it does not matter.
I also think of you as...
Neesan!
Jin!
Wow, so great, just like those old dramas.
I do not know him anymore!
I never would have thought that he would have a real interest in sisters...
How disgusting!
You traitor, Jin!
You are the worst!
Well, I fell in love with her.
Neesan, let us go to the ends of the earth together.
Yes...
What is wrong, Daitetsu?
We can talk in the living room...
S-Sorry, but I really wanted to make sure of one thing.
How do you feel about Nagi-san?
Huh?
How I feel?
I am not sure...
Well, I would like it if she had more normal taste buds.
She is your sister, right?
Your sister.
A real sister with actual proof, right?
Proof?
Then...
Well, I do not have any proof,
but she is definitely my sister.
My father always used to tell me that I had a sister...
Oh, really?
He used to say that?
I thought I remembered hearing that you only knew about her existence since only recently...
Shit!
Oh no, that was my mistake.
I was able to get in touch with my father.
Then he said she was definitely his daughter...
I see.
So your father is coming back.
Shit, shit!
Uh no, he is not coming back...
Shut your mouth!
He is been studying too hard and his memory is not really clear.
You will catch a cold like that, so please take a bath.
I have prepared a set of clothes in the living room, so please use it.
And so, Jin and I have to prepare dinner, so please excuse us.
You really suck at lying!
You should leave the consistency stuff to me!
Your lies are full of loopholes.
I cover it up with my great acting so there is no problem.
Oh?
Since we have publicized that I am your sister, we have to go on with me being your sister.
I will not accept having to leave here because of your stupid errors.
I know...
This house with only children and no parents is convenient.
You also let me do what I like as well.
This is between us, but you seem to be able to support me financially as well.
You just need to think about how to let me live comfortably.
What?
What is this?!
Being his sister was a lie?
Nagi-san is using this house for her convenience,
and Jin loves her.
In other words, this...
If you want me to tease you some more, pay up!
You hopeless guy!
Hopeless!
Jin is secretly paying tribute to an evil woman!
So, please eat up.
Itadakimasu.
Itadakimasu!
Behind her innocent mask, she is actually...
I will discipline you!
You mongrel, you mongrel!
Scary!
But I shall not be defeated!
I will protect Jin!
Oh Daitetsu, you do not have to be that reserved.
It was not Nagi who made this.
It is pouch-packed.
See, is not he suspicious of us?
Well, he always look this fierce...
I wonder.
Let us act like we are siblings from a happy family scene.
I guess so...
Jin, you are being rude.
You have a grain of rice stuck on your cheek.
That is dirty, Oneesan!
You deserve to be struck by lightning.
It is a waste of rice.
Well, that is true, but...
Besides, they say that seven gods reside in a single grain of rice.
You must consume them while greatly thanking the gods from above.
Look, there is another one here.
I can do it myself, Oneesan!
No.
But well...
Did not that just have the complete opposite effect?
I did it just like they did in TV anime.
Wait, is this something I should be getting involved in?
This is between a man and a woman.
If I intervene and mess things up...
Umm well...
Did this come out of the closet just now?
This is the Spirit of the Tree statue you were planning to exhibit in the city contest.
Do not tell me this guy...!
Come to think of it, the face on this statue...
Not at all!
Hey, is this Nagi-san?
He notices it!
Then, no more hiding and escaping!
I shall be prepared.
Yes, that statue is me!
It is me who is the Spirit of the Tree.
So it was like that.
So Nagi-san was the model.
He interpreted it like that?
What happened to that statue in the end?
Well, that was... umm...
I see.
It did not get finished.
I am sorry, since you went through the trouble of getting me the Holy Tree from the shrine.
Do not worry about it.
I did not ask for the Holy Tree.
Huh?
What do you mean?
Well, since you said you wanted to turn the Spirit you met as a child into a piece of art,
I actually... stole it.
Really?
You did that for me?
I am sorry about that.
I just thought I wanted to play a role in your passion.
So the sacred tree I secretly stole from the shrine...!
You deserve to be struck by lightning!
Huh?
Deja vu?
You stole it?!
Well, the construction people said they just were going to burn it.
I thought it would be a waste and-
That is called purifying by burning.
It means it would be disposed of ceremoniously.
Oh, really?
So you were the culprit who gave the sacred tree to Jin.
You thief!
A thief?
I was only doing it for Jin...
Shut up!
What do you think a sacred tree is?!
Why is Nagi-san so mad?
Even if she is an occult maniac, this is too outrageous!
This woman!
This man!
I hate her!
I hate him!
You will be cursed.
According to my research, those who steal the vessel of a god have a high probability of being cursed.
Being involved in accidents and criminal incidents.
Strange phenomena and cases where they are sickened and eventually die.
Cases like those are not uncommon.
If you reflect upon your actions and repent, you might be forgiven but...
If you do not show quite a great deal of sincerity...
It seems like Jin, who carved the statue, experienced strange phenomena.
Sooner or later, you too...
A dream?!
Unpleasantly realistic.
All because Nagi-san told me something like that!
Jin, wake up!
Huh?
The lights will not turn on!
Sooner or later, you too...
The circuit breaker did not trip.
I guess the neighborhood must have a blackout.
Nagi must have surprised him.
She said she would deliver divine punishment, but I hope she does not overdo it.
Oh, they came back on.
Hey Nagi, are you awake?
Hey, you did something to Daitetsu, did not you?
Nagi, wake up.
I am coming in.
Huh?
Nagi...
I just need to repent, right?
The shrine might be gone,
but will I make it on time?
I am sorry!
Please excuse me!
Please forgive me!
I will not do it anymore!
I deeply regret it!
I beg you, god!
Has that girl done something silly again?
You do not have to appologize.
What you want to do with chip of wood is all up to you.
Rather, you have done well.
Be grateful for the fate weaved by humans.
Good boy.
God...?
My body feels so damp.
You do not remember anything from last night?
It is not that I do not remember, but...
I slept normally and just woke up like this.
That is called not being able to remember!
Last night, Daitetsu carried you home while you were unconscious!
Do not you remember?
Ah, that is right...
Now that you mention it... yes.
What do you mean, after I mention it?
Different from dentures.
Do not get them wrong since they sound the same.
I know.
I understand.
You have gone unconcious like that before as well.
Are not you hiding something from me?
No, I am not hiding anything.
Do not lie!
You secretly went out to scare Daitetsu, did not you?
What exactly did you do?
Cut it out, okay?
He is not very good with ghosts and stuff.
And that aside, how could you go unconcious?
I have been thinking about this, but you are...
Shut up!
Stop prying!
I told you before!
Understand your place as a human!
Such a rude man!
Nagi says she remembers nothing.
Were you two hit by lightning?
No.
I cannot explain it well...
Umm... did Nagi do something?
Well, I think I have the answer, but...
No, I still cannot explain it well.
What is with her?
It pisses me off!
Did not something like this happen before?
It was right after she went unconscious.
I do not get it at all.
I do not get it at all.
Did a god really possess Nagi-san that time?
Since she does not seem to remember anything herself.
It does not sound like a lie either.
So scary!
So scary!
Still scary if it was a god.
What is with him?
Shh!
Do not look at him.
No, it is too quick to consider it a spiritual phenomenon.
During that time, Nagi-san said that I did not have to apologize.
She must have come to apologize for frightening me too much.
Yes.
That must be it.
After all, she is good at faking things.
That must have been acting.
How long are you going to be shitting?!
Even if it were an act, I still do not understand her intentions!
Is she planning something to hide her relationship with Jin?
Crap!
Am I being controlled by her tactics without noticing it?
Damn it, Jin!
Why did not you come talk to me?
Is your relationship with that woman really that important!?
Jin...
Mikuriya and Daitetsu-kun are acting strange?
Yes, they are...
They are not having a fight, but...
There is something awkward going on between them.
Ouch Daitetsu...
Huh?
Jin and Daitetsu-kun.
Jin, I am begging you!
What is going on?
I cannot hear well.
Let me hear it directly from your mouth.
About that...
I am sorry, Daitetsu!
I cannot answer that!
Wait, Jin!
It is just that I...
I wonder what it could be!
It is unusual for them to fall out!
Is not it?
The two did come to school together.
Maybe Daitetsu-kun stay over at Jin's house last night.
I guess something must have happened during that time...
Young boys!
The two of them!
Sleepover!
Hey Sempai, what are you saying?
It is just that I...
I would love to hear the following words!
Vice president, even you?!
We are just kidding.
Nagi-tan is there, so it is not like they were alone together.
Even if they were alone together, that would be impossible!
Cannot we just ask them directly?
But someone like me cannot...
I will not surrender Jin to you!
A god does not approve of a man such as you!
Huh?
Oh my.
Next time on Kannagi is... oops.
